         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>The illustrious Ciṟṟampalam. Jovian year Cārvati, month of Puraṭṭāci, 18 day, Saturday, third [lunar day], constellation of Aculaṉi: in this auspicious day the Periyapurāṇam [alias] Tiṟṟuttoṇṭarpurāṇam (emend into Tiṟuttoṇṭar°) is completed.</p>
